{"tid":535283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"汪 明 荃 籲 勿 看 淫 照 :「嚟 嚟 去 去 又 係 嗰 幾 招」","createTime":"2018-01-20T16:16:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T00:23:57.000Z","uid":24160,"like":99,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"1abbc5241dcabb66c305d05a02b5799b5072dbbb","tid":535283,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T16:16:57.000Z","msg":"近日的疑似藝人淫照風波除牽涉鍾欣桐、張栢芝和陳文媛外，陳冠希（Edison）的緋聞女友顏穎思及陳思慧昨日相繼牽連入內，逾200張床照同時湧現。汪明荃（阿姐）昨出席活動時對事件十分感慨，她呼籲女性在情到濃時做事要顧後果，否則斷送前途，阿姐又斥責拍攝淫照的人心理變態，而發放照片的人罪加一等。李詩韻則謂罷看照片，免傷害當事人，她不覺得發相者欲挑釁警方，只是可能很不喜歡當事人或該藝人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20080207/large/07ec1p2new.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20080207%2Flarge%2F07ec1p2new.jpg&h=e60ba712&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汪明荃呼籲女性不要在情到濃事做出不顧後果的事，更大罵影淫照的人心理變態。<br />\n<br />\n一時衝動<br />\n「明知傷害到人」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20080203/large/03ec1p3n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20080203%2Flarge%2F03ec1p3n.jpg&h=7ee115aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n汪明荃：「有乜嘢好睇？個個身體都係咁！」<br />\n汪明荃昨被問到有關有貌似栢芝的淫照時，指拉姑為此嬲怒十分正常。<br />\n<br />\n汪明荃昨日到天水圍出席活動時表示沒有看過網上淫照，她說：「真係好離譜，希望快啲拉到人，大家盡量都唔好睇，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有乜嘢好睇？個個身體都係咁。</span></span>」有人問阿姐有否慰問契仔謝霆鋒，她即鄭重澄清霆鋒非其契仔，並謂謝婷婷才是其契女。問到知否狄波拉是否很生氣，阿姐說：「拉姑嬲就一定㗎，不過我覺得時下年輕人唔能夠太開放，識朋友要小心啲，互聯網傷害真係好大，總之放上去嘅人就缺德，再睇又係缺德。」<br />\n<br />\n阿姐得知有200多張淫照出現，她即震驚道：「唔係啩，唔好好似去玩鬥多鬥氣咁，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有相嘅人快啲銷毀啦，傳閱都唔道德。啲人（指當事人）一時衝動做咗呢啲嘢，明知傷害到人，啲人仲要繼續發放，對當事人造成更大傷害。</span></span>」自從警方稱拘捕發相源頭後，再有大批淫照流出，似挑釁警方，阿姐謂：「既然拉咗人做咗嘢，我哋要信任警方，𠵱家已經傷害咗無數人，再放相上網嘅人就罪加一等，喺傷口上灑鹽，係缺德嘅行為，係個人操守，唔係貪得意嘅事，如果發生喺你家人身上，你都想保護佢啦，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">停止傳閱啲相啦，畀啲時間當事人克服難關。</span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n有傳將會有淫短片流出，有指女事主很難面對公眾，阿姐表示：「咁又唔會，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">嚟嚟去去又係嗰幾招，成年人都會做嘅嘢，只不過佢哋係公眾人物</span></span>，不過好慘，需要啲時間去面對，件事連家人同朋友都影響埋，科技發達唔係畀大家咁用，係去吸收正面信息，影嗰個人心理好有問題，係咪變態呢？所有女仔都要小心，情到濃時都要顧後果，𠵱家付上前途㖭！」汪也表示：「<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">人要有操守，不想被別人看就不要拍。</span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20080207/10730240\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20080207%2F10730240&d=VTVUaDvxTuXSvhzJp1u6B54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=b0f8c680\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20080207%2F10730240&h=76dfb598\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20080207/10730240</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20080203/10716664\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20080203%2F10716664&d=VTVUaDvxTuXSvhzJp1u6B54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=0f06d182\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20080203%2F10716664&h=f9a06b68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20080203/10716664</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/finance/daily/20080205/30238281\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2F20080205%2F30238281&d=VTVUaDvxTuXSvhzJp1u6B54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=ea4aad6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2F20080205%2F30238281&h=2832cf6b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/finance/daily/20080205/30238281</a>"},{"pid":"d6ce5abb0ee6c320e7f8cb0d6301d5a5cd82af71","tid":535283,"uid":24160,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T16:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056370180e8d6497018f0125e6cdaa2ae90bb5b5","tid":535283,"uid":24160,"like":79,"dislike":1,"score":78,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T16:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3o6Zt1R7o2NMMRPrP2/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3o6Zt1R7o2NMMRPrP2%2Fgiphy.gif&h=a54301a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3o6Zt1R7o2NMMRPrP2/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3o6Zt1R7o2NMMRPrP2%2Fgiphy.gif&h=a54301a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/3o6Zt1R7o2NMMRPrP2/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3o6Zt1R7o2NMMRPrP2%2Fgiphy.gif&h=a54301a7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b120d05ad6a2b9c9c0375378375398c7a64089c3","tid":535283,"uid":7840,"like":46,"dislike":3,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T16:34:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0aad5d631f61f19e2f2bf381ab16f897a0d2f023","tid":535283,"uid":17008,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T16:37:02.000Z","msg":"家英哥，用投擲地球！"},{"pid":"3c74923722880c6322deb45e735b863ff6ce509b","tid":535283,"uid":34251,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T16:38:30.000Z","msg":"第一張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蘋果照妖鏡名不虛傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" clas